+><H2
+>Name</H2
+>rdisc&nbsp;--&nbsp;network router discovery daemon</DIV
+><DIV
+CLASS="REFSYNOPSISDIV"
+><A
+NAME="AEN1030"
+></A
+><H2
+>Synopsis</H2
+><P
+><B
+CLASS="COMMAND"
+>rdisc</B
+>  [<CODE
+CLASS="OPTION"
+>-abdfstvV</CODE
+>] [<TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
