+><H1
+><A
+NAME="PING"
+></A
+>ping</H1
+><DIV
+CLASS="REFNAMEDIV"
+><A
+NAME="AEN8"
+></A
+><H2
+>Name</H2
+>ping, ping6&nbsp;--&nbsp;send ICMP ECHO_REQUEST to network hosts</DIV
+><DIV
+CLASS="REFSYNOPSISDIV"
+><A
+NAME="AEN11"
+></A
+><H2
+>Synopsis</H2
+><P
+><B
+CLASS="COMMAND"
+>ping</B
+>  [<CODE
+CLASS="OPTION"
+>-LRUbdfnqrvVaAB</CODE
+>] [-c <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>count</I
+></TT
+>] [-m <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>mark</I
