+>] [-l <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>preload</I
+></TT
+>] [-p <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>pattern</I
+></TT
+>] [-s <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>packetsize</I
+></TT
+>] [-t <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>ttl</I
+></TT
+>] [-w <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>deadline</I
+></TT
+>] [-F <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>flowlabel</I
+></TT
+>] [-I <TT
+CLASS="REPLACEABLE"
+><I
+>interface</I
+></TT
+>] [-M <TT
