+>YOSHIFUJI Hideaki
+&lt;yoshfuji@skbuff.net&gt;</A
+>.</P
+></DIV
+><DIV
+CLASS="REFSECT1"
+><A
+NAME="AEN585"
+></A
+><H2
+>SECURITY</H2
+><P
+><B
+CLASS="COMMAND"
+>arping</B
+> requires <CODE
+CLASS="CONSTANT"
+>CAP_NET_RAWIO</CODE
+> capability
+to be executed. It is not recommended to be used as set-uid root,
+because it allows user to modify ARP caches of neighbour hosts.</P
+></DIV
+><DIV
+CLASS="REFSECT1"
+><A
+NAME="AEN590"
+></A
+><H2
